---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="IV Sedation Dentistry Lethbridge | Able Family Dental"
  description="Moderate conscious IV sedation at Able Family Dental in Lethbridge. Ideal for severe dental anxiety, complex procedures, or a sensitive gag reflex. Dr. Tyler Snow certified."
>

  <!-- ============================================================
       HERO
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute right-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[42%] pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
      <img
        src="/images/services/hero-iv-sedation.jpg"
        alt=""
        width="800"
        height="600"
        loading="eager"
        decoding="async"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 w-2/3" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--color-brand-primary), transparent);"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-wide relative py-16 lg:py-24 lg:max-w-[64%]">
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-white mb-5" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/" class="text-white hover:text-white/80 transition-colors">Home</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <a href="/services/" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-colors">Services</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <a href="/services/sedation/" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-colors">Sedation</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <span class="text-white">IV Sedation</span>
      </nav>
      <p class="eyebrow text-white">Sedation Dentistry</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-5xl)] leading-tight text-white max-w-2xl">
        IV Sedation
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-[var(--color-text-on-dark-muted)] leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
        Moderate conscious IV sedation delivers the deepest level of in-office relaxation available — allowing patients with significant anxiety or complex treatment needs to receive care comfortably and safely.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       CONTENT
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="section-y bg-[var(--color-surface-cool)]">
    <div class="container-wide">

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-14">
        <p class="eyebrow">How it works</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-4xl)] leading-tight text-[var(--color-brand-primary)]">
          The deepest in-office sedation available
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          With IV sedation, sedative medication is delivered directly into your bloodstream through a small intravenous line, typically placed in the back of your hand or arm. The onset is rapid and the depth of sedation can be precisely controlled and adjusted by Dr. Snow throughout your appointment. You remain in a moderate conscious state — relaxed, largely unaware of the procedure, and able to breathe independently — while our team monitors your vital signs continuously.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-14">

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[var(--color-border-soft)] shadow-md flex flex-col">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shrink-0">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4.5 9.5V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v4.5"/><path d="M4.5 9.5a7.5 7.5 0 0 0 15 0"/><path d="M12 12v7"/><path d="M9 19h6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-2">Precise control</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed flex-1">Because the medication is delivered intravenously, Dr. Snow can titrate — gradually adjust — the dosage in real time. This means your level of sedation is always calibrated to keep you comfortable without over-sedating.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[var(--color-border-soft)] shadow-md flex flex-col">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shrink-0">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-2">Deeply relaxed</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed flex-1">Most patients are in such a deep state of relaxation that they have little or no memory of the procedure. IV sedation is often described as feeling like the appointment was over in minutes, even if it lasted much longer.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[var(--color-border-soft)] shadow-md flex flex-col">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shrink-0">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-2">Safe and monitored</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed flex-1">Your heart rate, blood pressure, and oxygen levels are monitored continuously throughout the procedure. Dr. Snow's certification ensures the highest standard of safety for every IV sedation appointment.</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Who is it for -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-[var(--color-border-soft)] shadow-md mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-3xl)] text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-4">Who is IV sedation for?</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
          IV sedation is the preferred option for patients who need a deeper level of comfort than nitrous oxide or oral sedation can provide. Dr. Tyler Snow is certified in moderate conscious IV sedation and will assess your suitability during a pre-treatment consultation. IV sedation is particularly well suited for patients who:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
          {[
            "Have severe or profound dental anxiety that prevents them from seeking care",
            "Need to complete multiple or complex treatments in a single visit",
            "Have a very sensitive gag reflex that makes dental work extremely difficult",
            "Have not responded adequately to nitrous oxide or oral sedation",
            "Have special needs or medical conditions that require enhanced comfort management",
            "Are undergoing lengthy surgical procedures such as multiple extractions or implant placement",
          ].map(item => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-sm leading-relaxed">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[var(--color-brand-accent)]" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Because the effects of IV sedation last longer than other options, you will need a responsible adult to drive you home and stay with you for the remainder of the day. Dr. Snow will provide complete pre- and post-operative instructions at your consultation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Dr. Snow credentials callout -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] rounded-2xl p-8 text-white">
        <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-2xl)] mb-3">Certified by Dr. Tyler Snow</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-on-dark-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          Dr. Snow holds certification in moderate conscious IV sedation, oral sedation, and nitrous oxide, as well as specialized training in caring for patients with dental anxiety. When you choose IV sedation at Able Family Dental, you are in the hands of a dentist with the credentials and experience to make your visit as safe and comfortable as possible.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       CTA BAND
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] py-16 text-center overflow-hidden relative">
    <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full pointer-events-none" viewBox="0 0 1440 160" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M0 60 C 240 20, 480 100, 720 60 C 960 20, 1200 100, 1440 60 L1440 160 L0 160 Z" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.03)"/>
    </svg>
    <div class="relative container-wide">
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-4xl)] text-white leading-tight">Ready to feel comfortable at the dentist?</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-[var(--color-text-on-dark-muted)] text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">Call <a href="tel:+14033277202" class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-[var(--color-brand-accent-soft)] transition-colors">403.327.7202</a> or request an appointment online.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/book/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Request an Appointment</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-lg border border-white/30 text-white hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
